<eesti>Olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tja </eesti>
<inglise>Undertaking with significant market power </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Sideamet tunnistab konkreetsel telekommunikatsiooniteenuseturul ja selle teenuse osutamise piirkonnas olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu operaatori v&otilde;i &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniteenuse osutaja: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Estonian National Estonian National Communications Board shall declare the public telecommunications network operator or public telecommunications service provider as the undertaking with significant market power in the relevant market of telecommunications services and in the area: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kellele on riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsuse poolt ainsana antud &otilde;igus (k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses ainu&otilde;igus) opereerida teatud &uuml;ldkasutatavat telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rku v&otilde;i osutada teatud &uuml;ldkasutatavat telekommunikatsiooniteenust v&otilde;i arendada mingit muud telekommunikatsioonialast tegevust kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud territooriumil; </eesti>
<inglise>1) who enjoys the exclusive right (for the purposes of this Act exclusive right) granted by the state or local government to operate specific public telecommunications network or provide specific public telecommunications services or develop any other activity relating to telecommunications in a defined territory; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kelle turuosa koos ema- ja t&uuml;tarettev&otilde;tjaga on v&auml;hemalt 25 protsenti konkreetse &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniteenuse turu k&auml;ibest v&otilde;i v&auml;hemalt 25 protsenti liiklusest sidumisteenuseturu korral ja kes ei t&otilde;enda, et selle turuosa omamine ei ohusta vaba konkurentsi. </eesti>
<inglise>2) whose market share together with the parent undertaking or subsidiary is at least 25 per cent of the turnover of the specific public telecommunications service market or at least 25 per cent of the traffic in the case of the interconnection service market and who does not prove that the holding of such market share does not prejudice free competition. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sideamet v&otilde;ib tunnistada olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu operaatori v&otilde;i &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniteenuse osutaja, kelle turuosa on konkreetse &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniteenuse turu k&auml;ibest v&auml;iksem kui 25 protsenti, kui see on p&otilde;hjendatav konkreetsete konkurentsitingimustega antud telekommunikatsiooniteenuseturul. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Estonian National Communications Board may declare a public telecommunications network operator or public telecommunications service provider whose market share is less than 25 per cent of the turnover of the specific public telecommunications service market to be the undertaking with significant market power if this is justified by concrete competition conditions in such telecommunications market. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideamet otsustab igal aastal telekommunikatsiooniteenuseturul olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks tunnistamise hiljemalt eelneva aasta 1. detsembriks. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Estonian National Communications Board shall decide each year the declaration of the undertaking with significant market power in the telecommunications service market no later than by 1 December of the previous year. </inglise>
<eesti>Sideameti peadirektori k&auml;skkirjas m&auml;rgitakse telekommunikatsiooniteenuseturul olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjate loetelu koos andmetega, millisel telekommunikatsiooniteenuseturul ja millises selle teenuse osutamise piirkonnas loetakse neid olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjateks. </eesti>
<inglise>The directive of the Director General of the Estonian National Communications Board shall specify a list of undertakings with significant market power in the telecommunications service market together with the information concerning the telecommunications service market and area in which such undertakings are declared to have significant market power. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Sideamet teatab kirjalikult koos p&otilde;hjendustega k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 1 punktis 2 ja l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks tunnistamise kavatsusest vastavale &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu operaatorile v&otilde;i telekommunikatsiooniteenuse osutajale v&auml;hemalt kaks kuud enne isiku olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks tunnistamise otsustamist. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Estonian National Communications Board shall notify the corresponding public telecommunications network operator or public telecommunications service provider in a reasoned manner in writing of its intention to declare the undertaking as an undertaking with significant market power specified in clause (1) 2) and subsection (2) of this section at least two months before the deciding to declare such person as the undertaking with significant market power. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) &Uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu operaator v&otilde;i &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniteenuse osutaja v&otilde;ib esitada Sideametile oma kirjaliku arvamuse enda olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks tunnistamise kavatsuse kohta k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatud t&auml;htaja jooksul, kui Sideamet ei ole arvamuse esitamiseks andnud pikemat t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A public telecommunications network operator or public telecommunications service provider may submit a written opinion to the Estonian National Communications Board on the intention to declare the operator or service provider as the undertaking with significant market power within the term specified in subsection (4) of this section unless the Estonian National Communications Board has provided a longer term for submitting an opinion. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks tunnistamist k&auml;sitleva Sideameti peadirektori k&auml;skkirja v&auml;ljav&otilde;te saadetakse Konkurentsiametile. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) An extract of the directive of the Estonian National Communications Board on the declaration of an undertaking as the undertaking with significant market power shall be sent to the Competitions Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 3 nimetatud k&auml;skkirja v&auml;ljav&otilde;te saadetakse olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjale. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) An extract of the directive specified in subsection (3) of this section shall be sent to the undertaking with significant market power. </inglise>
<eesti>Olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjate loetelu avaldatakse ametlikus v&auml;ljaandes Ametlikud Teadaanded. </eesti>
<inglise>The list of undertakings with significant market power shall be published in the official publication Ametlikud Teadaanded (2). </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks tunnistatud &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu operaator v&otilde;i &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniteenuse osutaja peab oma tegevuse &uuml;he kuu jooksul, arvates olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjaks tunnistamise k&auml;skkirja v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte avaldamisest k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 7 s&auml;testatud viisil, viima vastavusse olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tjale k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) A public telecommunications network operators or public telecommunications service provider who has been declared as the undertaking with significant market power shall make its activities to comply with the requirements established for undertakings with significant market power in this Act within one month after publication, in a manner established in subsection (7) of this section, of the extract of the directive concerning the declaration as the undertaking with significant market power. </inglise>
<eesti>(9) Juhul kui &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu operaatori v&otilde;i &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniteenuse osutaja turuosa on v&auml;hemalt 40 protsenti konkreetse &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniteenuse turu k&auml;ibest, reguleerib tema kui turgu valitseva ettev&otilde;tja tegevust lisaks k&auml;esolevale seadusele konkurentsiseadus (RT I 1998, 30, 410; 1999, 89, 813). </eesti>
<inglise>(9) If the market share of a public telecommunications network operator or public telecommunications service provider is at least 40 per cent of the turnover of the specific public telecommunications service market, the activities of the operator or service provider as the undertaking with significant market power shall be governed by the Competition Act (RT I 1998, 30, 410; 1999, 89, 813), in addition to this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Turgu valitsevale ettev&otilde;tjale kohaldatakse olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tja kohta k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatut. </eesti>
<inglise>The provisions of this Act concerning the undertaking with significant market power apply to an undertaking dominating the market. </inglise>
<eesti>(10) Konkurentsitingimuste hindamise ja telekommunikatsiooniteenuseturgude piiritlemise korra olulise turuj&otilde;uga ettev&otilde;tja m&auml;&auml;ramiseks kehtestab teede- ja sideminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(10) The Minister of Transport and Communications shall establish the procedure for estimating competition conditions and specifying telecommunications service markets for the assignment of undertakings with significant market power. </inglise>
